  			</div>
  		</div><div>
  			<div id="item-1824"><p>Hi &#8220;Mom,&#8221;<br />
I like your blog &#8212; primarily because Martha Stewart makes my lips involuntarily curl.  But I have a tremendous recipe for caramel nut bars, which sounds a lot like Martha&#8217;s, only easier. I make them all the time &#8212; they&#8217;re by far my most requested cookie.  I just made a batch last night.  If you&#8217;d like to try them, please let me know via my blog or email and I&#8217;ll be happy to send it along!  (All on one page &#8212; so you won&#8217;t have to flip anything)  :)</p></div>
