  			</div>
  		</div><div>
  			<div id="item-1825"><p>I am really sorry to hear about your oozing nut bars. I made them this weekend and they worked out great. I agere about the problem with having to turn the pages, but I cook out of that book all the time and everything seems to work like a dream. Good luck :)</p></div>
